<causal_agent wordnetid="100007347" confidence="0.8">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../796/44796.xml">
Giovanni Falcone</link></causal_agent>
</official>
</worker>
</judge>
</person>
</adjudicator>
</physical_entity>
</skilled_worker>
 and began his life as an informant. </p>

